{"tid":2029741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港一國一制，蔡英文再一次榮登國際頭條","createTime":"2020-05-22T11:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T11:28:06.000Z","uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c16bd20fbab998cdbeb6657f54b79c377c14f30e","tid":2029741,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"Sources: Goodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際送子彈，極速射到<br />\n<br />\n「國際送子彈」報導系列，啱啱半個鐘前射到，有啲應該未收到，睇下有咩反應先。<br />\n<br />\n《The New York Times》<br />\nChina Pushes New Security Law for Hong Kong, Increasing Party&rsquo;s Sway<br />\n<a href=\"https://nyti.ms/2TuIarE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnyti.ms%2F2TuIarE&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=57f86e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nyti.ms/2TuIarE</a><br />\n<br />\n//The process would effectively circumvent the Hong Kong government, undercutting the relative autonomy granted to the territory under a political formula known as &ldquo;one country, two systems.&rdquo;//<br />\n（個做法明顯要撓過香港政府，削弱所謂「一國兩制」之下叫做有啲嘅自治權。）<br />\n<br />\n《BBC》<br />\nChina proposes controversial Hong Kong security law<br />\n<a href=\"https://bbc.in/3g9Qoiy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbc.in%2F3g9Qoiy&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=fc0f6809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbc.in/3g9Qoiy</a><br />\n<br />\n//Will the law draw protests?<br />\nIt is almost certain to do so, both in Hong Kong and abroad.//<br />\n（會唔引發抗爭？肯定會啦，仲要香港同海外一齊呀。）<br />\n<br />\n《The Guardian》<br />\nChina proposes controversial national security law for Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2yr9b84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yr9b84&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=ca414313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2yr9b84</a><br />\n<br />\n//The largely rubber-stamp body kicks off its full annual session on Friday in Beijing.On Thursday evening the National People&rsquo;s Congress confirmed its agenda would discuss &ldquo;establishing &amp; improving the legal system &amp; enforcement mechanisms for Hong Kong to safeguard national security&rdquo;//<br />\n（個橡皮圖章議會聽日開始，議程已公布咗討論所謂「建立同改進香港嘅法治同執法制度，保障國家安全」。）<br />\n<br />\n《The Washington Post》<br />\nChina to impose sweeping national security law in Hong Kong, bypassing city&rsquo;s legislature<br />\n<a href=\"https://wapo.st/36nC2Xd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwapo.st%2F36nC2Xd&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=b091af46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wapo.st/36nC2Xd</a><br />\n<br />\n//For the United States to treat Hong Kong as a separate entity, mostly for commercial purposes, the State Department must certify that the city retains &ldquo;a high degree of autonomy&rdquo; from China. Pompeo said its latest decision on this was still pending.//<br />\n（對於美國黎講，將香港視為獨立個體嘅主要原因，係要美國國務院認為香港可以保持「高度自治」，不過Pompeo話依家就要諗清楚喇。）<br />\n<br />\n《Rueters》<br />\nChina supports 'improvement' of Hong Kong's political system<br />\n<a href=\"https://reut.rs/3bXBgSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freut.rs%2F3bXBgSc&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=d8faa831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reut.rs/3bXBgSc</a><br />\n<br />\n//The high degree of autonomy promised to Hong Kong for 50 years under the &ldquo;one country, two systems&rdquo; arrangement has helped it thrive as a financial centre, while Macau is a major gambling centre.//<br />\n（「一國兩制」之下「五十年不變」呢個承諾，係令香港成為國際金融中心嘅原因，澳門？靠賭㗎喎！）<br />\n<br />\n#唔該大膽啲<br />\n#直接宣布一國一制<br />\n#正式確認違反中英聯合聲明<br />\n#唔做正YY<br />\n<br />\n*********************************<br />\n支持Patreon係本Page嘅支柱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/goodbyehkhellouk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=348958b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/goodbyehkhellouk</a><br />\nYouTube 新片：<br />\n《Juan Guaido：Rise to the Challenge》<br />\n「委內瑞拉代總統Juan Guaido：：國民唔堅持同覺悟，哪怕幾有執政意志，都可以係困局」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GoodbyeHKHelloUK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FGoodbyeHKHelloUK&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=818bb7e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/GoodbyeHKHelloUK</a><br />\n*********************************<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AnRX110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAnRX110.jpg&h=5496e2a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ra2tG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ra2tG2.jpg&h=5255d1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWa2tG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWa2tG7.jpg&h=976bd71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqhXhAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqhXhAy.jpg&h=589eaab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgqRm2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgqRm2f.jpg&h=85d8c314&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0058235afd4bbb532ed23aefdc1459cf3e8a4287","tid":2029741,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同場加映：<br />\n霸氣蔡英文連任大典堪稱荷里活大片</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗咁有戲劇感呀？<br />\n（嗱，無話型㗎！）<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文星期三正式就任總統，成為國際新聞一啲都唔出奇。坦白講，啲內容華文傳媒用中文報導得更直接精準，無謂英文譯返中文咁啦（不過，識英文係好重要，講三次！）。<br />\n<br />\n不過明明有好多官方或者攝影記者嘅相，點解偏偏咁多個國際媒體都要用呢張呢？喂呀，北面嗰啲無謂講喇，咁叫香港人又如何不比較呢？<br />\n<br />\n#有比較就有傷害<br />\n<br />\n用呢張相嘅報導：<br />\n《Financial Times》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/9fe5f9fc-1d4c-4bd9-b4d6-d05ff914d550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F9fe5f9fc-1d4c-4bd9-b4d6-d05ff914d550&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=c5143156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/9fe5f9fc-1d4c-4bd9-b4d6-d05ff914d550</a><br />\n《The Telegraph》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/05/20/taiwans-president-rejects-chinese-rule-amid-coronavirus-success/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2020%2F05%2F20%2Ftaiwans-president-rejects-chinese-rule-amid-coronavirus-success%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=07023b6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/05/20/taiwans-president-rejects-chinese-rule-amid-coronavirus-success/</a><br />\n《AFP》<br />\n<a href=\"https://business.facebook.com/creatorstudio/?tab=home&amp;mode=facebook&amp;collection_id=all_pages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.facebook.com%2Fcreatorstudio%2F%3Ftab%3Dhome%26mode%3Dfacebook%26collection_id%3Dall_pages&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4b593577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://business.facebook.com/creatorstudio/?tab=home&amp;mode=facebook&amp;collection_id=all_pages</a><br />\n《LA Times》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2020-05-20/taiwan-president-calls-for-stability-in-china-relations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fworld-nation%2Fstory%2F2020-05-20%2Ftaiwan-president-calls-for-stability-in-china-relations&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=871389ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2020-05-20/taiwan-president-calls-for-stability-in-china-relations</a><br />\n《DW News》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dw.com/en/china-reunification-inevitable-as-taiwans-tsai-starts-second-term-in-office/a-53504220\" data-sr-url=\